After you unzip the pp1.zip file, cd to UnigramProject folder.

Run execution command: java -jar pp1.jar

This command will output the results for the project.
If you need to check details of the code, run command cd src/imogramproject
I have five .java files for this project.
Unigram.java includes all probabilities functions, parse file functions and the main function for this project.
Equations.java contains all helpful functions given from the project
Task1.java defines the tests for task1
Task2.java defines the tests for task2
Task3.java defines the tests for task3

